<p>Register赋值</p>
<figure class="highlight angelscript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">PQRSTUVWa</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0</span>:  <span class="number">50</span>      push  eax</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span>:  <span class="number">51</span>      push  ecx</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2</span>:  <span class="number">52</span>      push  edx  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">3</span>:  <span class="number">53</span>      push  ebx</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">4</span>:  <span class="number">54</span>      push  esp</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">5</span>:  <span class="number">55</span>      push  ebp</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">6</span>:  <span class="number">56</span>      push  esi</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">7</span>:  <span class="number">57</span>      push  edi</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">8</span>:  <span class="number">61</span>      popa</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

